quagga.predicted.text: The performance testing guidelines we used on the TECO and Linden #6
contracts include wording for liquid fuel machines.  We could substitute
exhibit F in it's entirety or replace the missing sections that address
liquid fuel.

Subject: Change Order #3 to Add Dual Fuel to Unit #2 in BlueDog Contract
